item.title: Web Analytics: Analyzing clickstream of 160,000 visitors
item.description: This project is carried out by me for a university assignment. The dataset is a randomly generated visitor clickstream to a website of a company. All codes and explanations, along with the dataset, are present in my GitHub repository.
